author: Newley Purnell
title: Tata Consultancy Services Profit Rose 14.5% in Second Quarter
text:
BANGALORE, India—India’s Tata Consultancy Services Ltd. on Tuesday reported a 14.5% rise in its fiscal second-quarter net profit, driven by strong demand from North America and the U.K. as it focuses on offering new kinds of technological services.
